  "readme_html": "\n        \n          <p><img src=\"/assets/library/command-r7b-arabic/e96310ca-5a9a-4e86-8eda-5a0a68513fc6\"/></p>\n\n<p>Command R7B Arabic is a fast and highly efficient model that can be served on low-end GPUs, a MacBook, or even CPUs. Similar to other models in the R series, it offers a context length of 128k and industry-leading performance in its class across capabilities that matter most to businesses like regional language understanding and strong accuracy with citations using retrieval-augmented generation (RAG). Its compact size enables businesses to more easily scale Arabic language AI applications to production.</p>\n\n<h2>References</h2>\n\n<p><a href=\"https://cohere.com/blog/command-r7b-arabic\" rel=\"nofollow\">Blog Post</a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"https://huggingface.co/CohereForAI/c4ai-command-r7b-arabic-02-2025\" rel=\"nofollow\">Hugging Face</a></p>\n\n        \n      ",
